\newlabel{fig:example_2d}{{7}{20}{Two-dimensional spatial experiment with $N_\theta =64$ trait grid points. Left: spatial marginal density $\rho _\varepsilon (t, x,y)$ at $t=20$. Right: trait marginal $P_\varepsilon (t, \theta )$ at $t=20$}{figure.7}{}}
